# thermodynamics.sakphys - Sakum physics: Thermodynamics
# domain=Physics/Thermodynamics  format=sakphys

# --- Laws ---
ऊष्मागतिकी_१ ΔU = Q - W
ऊष्मागतिकी_२ ΔS_universe ≥ 0
ऊष्मागतिकी_० T → 0 ⇒ S → S_min

# --- Ideal gas ---
आदर्श_गैस P V = n R T

# --- Entropy ---
एन्ट्रॉपी dS = δQ_rev / T

